{"tid":1142071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"竊賊爆茶餐廳 偷走家居電話逃去","createTime":"2019-05-07T00:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T00:35:06.000Z","uid":3090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b089f6be8ed4f7105eac884ef4cca6e8786db4","tid":1142071,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StiTQqH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStiTQqH.png&h=3fee5f15&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hU8sUSo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhU8sUSo.png&h=ebce5f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油麻地長樂街6號一間茶餐廳，凌晨5時許，負責人返回開市，發現店內遭賊人潛入搜掠，後門門鎖遭撬毀，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，經初步點算，發現失去一部家居電話，相信賊人從毗鄰地盤天井爬入餐廳爆竊，離開時撬後門逃去，警方列作爆竊案件展開調查。"},{"pid":"947589a3b23ebcf949e6dc0e28f73ddbf9f8afc2","tid":1142071,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:33:53.000Z","msg":"高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749561cbfe5ad173c1ddaf5c565a9bca1ba1f4b6","tid":1142071,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T00:35:06.000Z","msg":"偷古董<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}